text: Lyakhovo () is a rural locality (a village) in Spartaksky Selsoviet, Yermekeyevsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 12 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 18 km from Yermekeyevo, 2 km from Spartak. == References == Category:Rural localities in Yermekeyevsky District
title: Lyakhovo, Yermekeyevsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
